Early Access Review

Brawlhalla;

Very simple 2D game that is a lot like SSB. You get put on a little map with 3 other people and you try to knock eachother off the edge to score points. You can buy more characters with ingame gold or you can just use the free character rotation. For being a game that is in early access it is very well made. The nice thing is it's a very small sized game so it doesn't really take much to run it. Definitely recommend this to anyone who is a fan of SSB or just 2D fighter games in general.

Final Verdict;

10/10
